==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cheetah
<hw>Chee"tah</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind.
<ets>ch⟦imac⟧t⟦amac⟧</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A species of
leopard (<spn>Cyn⟦ae⟧lurus jubatus</spn>) tamed and used for hunting in
India. The woolly cheetah of South Africa is <spn>Cyn⟦ae⟧lurus
laneus</spn>. It runs very fast in short spurts while hunting.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>chetah</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

